CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page A20, reads: "Maurice Contay of the Biblical Press, Inc., family Bible distributors, tells visitors about the 'Ideal Easter Gift.' Fred Benzenhoefer and Albert J. Merhaut assist."
TitMainTitle: Maurice Contay showing bible to two women wearing hats in Biblical Press Incorporated booth, with Fred Benzenhoefer and Albert J. Merhaut seated at tables, in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
